title: Organoplatinum(II) Type II Immunogenic Cell Death Inducers Target Protein Tyrosine Phosphatase 1B to Drive Immunogenicity.
abstract: Immunogenic cell death (ICD) inducers are valuable chemotherapeutic agents that elicit protective immune responses against tumors.
